{"tid":832752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵奇觀】內地女西九站落車即吐痰  一腳往返兩地成打卡熱點","createTime":"2018-09-23T04:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:49:30.000Z","uid":16697,"like":3,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ffea83039b1be802b3762bfa730b26369de241","tid":832752,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:21:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180923&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58713870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180923%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58713870&d=3MLEuntUU0VPnla4ey6UyDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f2562b93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180923%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58713870&h=b2720ef7\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180923&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58713870</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180923/large/1537663342_3bda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180923%2Flarge%2F1537663342_3bda.jpg&h=b039fa60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣深港高鐵香港段今日通車，《蘋果》記者今晨6時許就抵達廣州南站，直擊第一班車的情況，不僅看到了中港兩地車站規矩的大不同，還目擊到乘客在月台吐痰的嚇人情景，見證兩地文化的差異！<br />\n<br />\n廣州南站離市區甚遠，記者實測從越秀區鬧市，乘搭地鐵到廣州南站，需近30分鐘地鐵車程；按百度地圖顯示，從天河區、海珠區等市中心乘搭地鐵到廣州南站，行程均為約30分鐘。而在廣州南站月台上，記者發現，一名男子正在吸煙。原來，內地車站的規例與香港大不同，西九龍站內是禁止吸煙的，但廣州南站和深圳北站均無此規定。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n記者登車後，6時48分，列車開出，7時43分準時抵港。不過，甫落車，記者就看到嚇人一幕，有女乘客落車踏上月台後，即吐出一口濃痰！根據港鐵相關附屬法例，任何人不得在鐵路處所的任何部份吐痰，否則可被罰款5,000港元。</span><br />\n<br />\n廣州南下第一班高鐵抵達西九龍站，旅客還是非常興奮，內地口岸區與香港口岸區的分界線，成為了打卡熱點，不少乘客跨過地上的黃黑色分界線，拍下「一腳往返兩地」的照片留念。<br />\n《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"1e91234c6db85f2f5322c7badd6490ef6b7f24e9","tid":832752,"uid":173286,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"D 畜生都係周圍痾尿劃地盤架啦，大驚小怪.."},{"pid":"61d7021ab2c0d6f46f25d7ee6867574d7bb572f1","tid":832752,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4815125978b37677f90266eb18686df4378c65","tid":832752,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"人地中國人 你敢罰咩！<br />\n垃圾政府"},{"pid":"1584bc1587a7a51a9955baa2fa35db3ed1798b5b","tid":832752,"uid":111253,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"2018年啲生蕃依舊未進化過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df59514d6e3b79194a45d1ab205e6f36f1aba206","tid":832752,"uid":10757,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"冇野冇野 得個知字姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe2bf8b56b9914a823ab5bb9f0d56f36c6b0654","tid":832752,"uid":94824,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:41:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母毒果又搵人做媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5982e460c6484acc3cb4617e147d861ed84d09c1","tid":832752,"uid":77277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df59514d6e3b79194a45d1ab205e6f36f1aba206","tid":832752,"uid":10757,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"冇野冇野 得個知字姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"咦聽你口音，你湖北架？"},{"pid":"3b88e342097e8935606d4568b4726a2cefe02268","tid":832752,"uid":64621,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"月台係支那管㗎<br />\n港鐵附例點有效呀！<br />\n條鐵全段都係支那境或者割咗做支那境<br